          <mainBody>
            <p><span style="color:#0070C0"><b>Annex A – Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></span></p>
            <p><span style="color:#000000">The Act extends to England and Wales and applies to England only.</span></p>
            <table uk:widths="1.19in 1.07in 1.07in 1.07in 1.47in">
              <tr>
                <th>
